622
00:35:14,000 --> 00:35:15,000
Oh, the chicken soup.

623
00:35:15,000 --> 00:35:17,000
Martha said you came home
with the flu.

624
00:35:17,000 --> 00:35:19,000
Go back to sleep.

625
00:35:27,000 --> 00:35:31,000
Oh, and, um...
these are your glasses.

626
00:35:31,000 --> 00:35:33,000
I took them off.

627
00:35:35,000 --> 00:35:37,000
