don't do that.

657
00:37:36,000 --> 00:37:38,000
You can't sleep...
it's afternoon.

658
00:37:38,000 --> 00:37:40,000
Get up. Get dressed.

659
00:37:40,000 --> 00:37:41,000
Oh! Ooh...

660
00:37:43,000 --> 00:37:44,000
Mom?

661
00:37:48,000 --> 00:37:49,000
Mom?

662
00:37:51,000 --> 00:37:54,000
It was all my fault.

663
00:38:04,000 --> 00:38:07,000
( Julia crying )

664
00:38:10,000 --> 00:38:12,000
( gasping )

665
00:38:14,000 --> 00:38:17,000
( quietly ):
Amy, I'm here.

666
00:38:17,000 --> 00:38:18,000
Okay...

667
00:38:24,000 --> 00:38:26,000
Come on, David,
pick up.

668
00:38:26,000 --> 00:38:29,000
Please pick up.

669
00:39:07,000 --> 00:39:08,000
She seems stable.

670
00:39:08,000 --> 00:39:10,000
You can call me in the
morning if you want.

671
00:39:10,000 --> 00:39:12,000
This was a bad one.

672
00:39:12,000 --> 00:39:14,000
It was like she couldn't
catch her breath

673
00:39:14,000 --> 00:39:16,000
you know, like
she'd been running.

674
00:39:16,000 --> 00:39:19,000
Her lungs are small,
you know that.

675
00:39:19,000 --> 00:39:20,000
She's growing,
and they're not.

676
00:39:20,000 --> 00:39:23,000
I used to pray
for her to grow.

677
00:39:23,000 --> 00:39:25,000
When she was born,
she was so tiny.

678
00:39:25,000 --> 00:39:27,000
I was afraid to touch her
after the surgery, you know?

679
00:39:27,000 --> 00:39:30,000
I just knew I was hurting her
every time I picked her up.

680
00:39:30,000 --> 00:39:32,000
I remember talking
out loud to myself...

681
00:39:32,000 --> 00:39:37,000
shouting, really...
usually at Mark.

682
00:39:37,000 --> 00:39:40,000
Now I just... want her
to stay the same size

683
00:39:40,000 --> 00:39:43,000
and not grow an inch.

684
00:39:43,000 --> 00:39:45,000
What about Mark?

685
00:39:45,000 --> 00:39:47,000
I don't think
about Mark anymore.

686
00:39:50,000 --> 00:39:55,000
I'm sorry I made you
come out in the rain.

687
00:39:55,000 --> 00:39:57,000
( thunder rumbling in distance)

688
00:39:57,000 --> 00:39:59,000
Don't be afraid
to call me again tonight.

689
00:39:59,000 --> 00:40:00,000
Okay, thanks.

690
00:40:00,000 --> 00:40:01,000
And try to get
some sleep yourself.

691
00:40:01,000 --> 00:40:03,000
All right. Good night.

692
00:40:03,000 --> 00:40:04,000
Okay.

